The bot is hit in the head by the pincers, stumbling forward. He spins around with amazing speed, his battle centers taking over. Two very bug missile launchers flip over his shoulder and fire a missile each at the ground where Repugnus was standing and the cealing above him, the bot's eyes narrowing as the effect of the alchoholic energon in him lessens significantly.
